\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Thomas Muenzer was born in Stolberg, in the Harz, in 1498. It is said that his father died on the scaffold, a victim of the wilfulness of the Count of Stolberg.}{ }
\par\plain 
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0 Mediaeval mystics, especially the chiliastic works of Joachim of Calabria,}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.marxists.org/archive/marx/works/1850/peasant-war-germany/notes.htm#14"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0\super [}}{\f0\fs24\b0\ul\ulc0\super\cf4 14]}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~were the main subject of his studies}{ }
